divs: Sighting DetailsMy 15 year old daughter first spotted some kind of "craft" she describes as having colorful (red, blue, white and yellow) blinking lights in western corner of sky (near full moon)-- she called me outside: "Hurry it's going so fast!" I arrived just in time to see it blink red and white and "zig" a dramatic upward movement before quickly disappearing behind the hill to the east of our backyard. Just wondering if anyone else saw this??
Summary: low flying craft with blinking lights and erratic flight pattern
